# =============================================================================
# frontend 환경 변수 (Next.js)
# =============================================================================
#
# 로컬: `.env.local` — `npm run dev`
#
# Vercel 배포 (jeonsanghoon/techvalley_project):
#   Project → Settings → Environment Variables
#   • Name: NEXT_PUBLIC_AG_GRID_LICENSE_KEY
#   • Production / Preview / Development 모두 체크
#   저장 후 Redeploy (변수만 추가하고 재배포하지 않으면 반영되지 않음)
#
# Vercel 프로젝트 설정:
#   • Framework Preset: Next.js
#   • Root Directory: . (저장소 루트)
#   • Build Command: npm run build (기본값)
#   • Install Command: npm ci (기본값)
#
# =============================================================================

# AG Grid Enterprise + AG Charts Enterprise 라이선스 키
# https://www.ag-grid.com/license-pricing/
NEXT_PUBLIC_AG_GRID_LICENSE_KEY=your_ag_grid_enterprise_license_key_here

# Google Maps JavaScript API
# https://console.cloud.google.com/google/maps-apis/
NEXT_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=your_google_maps_api_key_here
